{"tid":304521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：對北韓核計畫忍耐結束","createTime":"2017-07-01T03:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T07:54:34.000Z","uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11f6a02f36a216f0196d8079516889f23389e7ac","tid":304521,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】美國總統特朗普在白宮與到訪的南韓總統文在寅會談時表示，美國對於北韓發展核計畫已經失去耐心。<br />\n<br />\n　　特朗普表示，他無心就此與不尊重人命的北韓政權尋求外交手段解決。他指出，「我們正面臨北韓魯莽和殘暴政權的威脅，這個政權的核計畫須面對我們果斷的回應。」<br />\n<br />\n　　特朗普在白宮玫瑰花園的記者會中指出，與北韓政權戰略性忍耐的時代已經失敗，且已失敗多年，又指對其忍耐已經結束。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打未架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便貼下首幾應景既改詞歌 &lt;終無焰&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PeUOMXI13Oo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPeUOMXI13Oo&d=O4NmLS%2FYfOScxcF7ZsI6K8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e37616ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PeUOMXI13Oo</a><br />\n<br />\n原post link <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/216810/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/216810/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"108e6e00df57bf57565b15ecd9e93b256ba27fbd","tid":304521,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49630e7b58b049f3b03240f2900abbba3c50bb66","tid":304521,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:26:53.000Z","msg":"Twitter見"},{"pid":"64e9dbba44a32f8ba59f182c90907052e93b7aae","tid":304521,"uid":47279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615ce587462a9b58c83c0fb7dcb5fff49502704d","tid":304521,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"學埋哂中國口交部d 野<